Write a program to scan the string from the user and to print it.

Input Format:

Input consist of 1 string.
Sample Input & Output:

Hello World

The string is Hello World

import java.util.Scanner;
public class Main
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        //creating an object for scanner class
        Scanner sc=  new Scanner(System.in);
        
        //initializing the variables and getting user input
        String input = sc.nextLine();
        
        System.out.print("The string is "+ input);
    }
}
